        <p>For the field &ldquo;Date appointment ended&rdquo; where a governance professional has a fixed-term appointment, enter the date their fixed appointment is due to end. If they do not have a fixed-term appointment, leave this field blank until their appointment ends and then add the date their appointment ended.</p>

        <p>Depending on the establishment or academy trust the governance professional is associated with will determine the type that can be selected (see table 4.9.1).</p>

        <p>For academies or free schools within a multi-academy trust, the selected governance sharing option will affect the type of governance professional that can be selected.</p>

