        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">5. Bulk update: Add or update governance information</h2>
        <p>Governance bulk update allows you to download your local authority-maintained school, academy, free school or academy trust&rsquo;s existing data (if any) and create new records or amend existing records and bulk upload the changes.</p>
        <p>If you&rsquo;re an establishment user, you can only upload governance data for your own establishment.</p>
        <p>If you are a MAT user, you can upload governance data for your own MAT.</p>
        <p>It is not possible to upload or update details of shared governance roles using bulk update.</p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">5.1 The process for bulk updating</h3>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
            <li>Select &lsquo;Tools&rsquo; from the menu at the top of the page</li>
            <li>In the &lsquo;Update&rsquo; section, select &lsquo;Bulk update governance&rsquo;</li>
            <li>Using the link provided, download the template (XLSX). If you have already provided some governance information the template will be prepopulated with your data</li>
            <li>You can edit existing data by updating the required field within the spreadsheet. <b>Please do not edit the column labelled &lsquo;GID&rsquo;</b></li>
            <li>If your file contains details of deleted governors, they will need to be removed before you can upload your amended spreadsheet to the system</li>
            <li>Use blank rows to add new records. You should provide either the unique reference number (URN) for the school or academy or the UID (provided on the academy trust record) for the MAT and complete all the required fields (see section 4). For new records including the initial import of records <b>please leave the column labelled &lsquo;GID&rsquo; blank</b></li>
            <li>To replace a &lsquo;fixed role&rsquo; (chair of governors, chair of trustees, accounting officer or chief financial officer) please add these details to a blank row. The original record for this role will be automatically archived when the template is uploaded</li>
            <li>Once you have completed all the required information save your template, then upload it for validation</li>
            <li>If your file is successfully validated, you can then complete the upload of your governance data</li>
            <li>If your file is not successfully validated, please download the results. The fields that failed validation will be highlighted in red. Please correct these entries and return to step 8 above.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">6. Historic data</h2>
        <p>Governance information for any of the governance roles where the term of office has ended within the last 12 months will be automatically archived to the section &lsquo;Historic (left within past 12 months)&rsquo;.</p>

        <p>Governance information for any of the governance roles where the term of office ended more than 12 months ago will be automatically archived and removed from public view.</p>

